author: Jared Gunther

text: Best price around when someone else wouldn't cooperate with me despite our past dealings on even extremely in demand high price tag items! I payed for a week shipping but when he got them a little later than expected he payed to make up for the delay with priority mail! Love my new hks cam gears. Definitely a great place to go.
